{"data":[{"date":"07:52 03/07","title":"Su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/suyt-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-bi-nhat-ban-lap-ky-luc-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Su\u00fdt t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00e0 chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c m\u1edbi trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup. </h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Bi-vuot-qua-Nhat-vao-tu-ket.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-nhat-ban-461-190228.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 0-2 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7p 2 ch\u1ec9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Haraguchi. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhat Ban lap ky luc voi ban thang cua Haraguchi vao luoi DT Bi.\" title=\"Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Haraguchi v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/suyt-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-bi-nhat-ban-lap-ky-luc-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Haraguchi v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2002. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2002 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. T\u00e1m n\u0103m sau, &quot;samurai xanh&quot; c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Paraguay v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-0 v\u00e0 thua 3-5 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c khi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup c\u00f3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini v\u00e0 Nacer Chadli.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Opta ph\u00e2n t\u00edch s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u World Cup m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chi ti\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c l\u00e0 n\u0103m 1966, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Jan Vertonghen l\u00e0 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1 ly xa nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u (18.6) m\u00e9t.</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c m\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Ngo\u00e0i k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp t\u1eeb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Haraguchi, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Takashi Inui. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2002 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cac-cuu-danh-thu-len-tieng-khi-bi-thang-kich-tinh-nhat-ban-465-190232.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/cac-cuu-danh-thu-len-tieng-khi-bi-thang-kich-tinh-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cac-cuu-danh-thu-len-tieng-khi-bi-thang-kich-tinh-nhat-ban-465-190232.html\">M\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t danh th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1c khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c danh th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u00ecm n\u1ed5i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh gi\u1eefa B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Rivaldo khi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2002. \u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p th\u00fa v\u1ecb l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (s\u00e2n Kobe Wing, Kobe).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, sau \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1996. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 5-3 t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 1966. Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean khi \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0 ch\u1ec9 sau 25 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-32-nhat-ban-quy-do-no-samurai-loi-cam-on-421-190243.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-phat-bieu-ve-tran-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190238.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, HLV B\u1ec9 n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban-421-190237.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-thua-nhan-bi-tung-run-so-nhat-ban-465-190236.html\">Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi-465-190233.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"837","checkdouble":"190240"},{"date":"07:22 03/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/du-am-bi-32-nhat-ban-quy-do-no-samurai-loi-cam-on.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. Ri\u00eang v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/274945/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00f3t tim</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i d\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, ai \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 World Cup c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 c\u00e1i l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch h\u1ee3p l\u00fd cho di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Rostov Arena \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 2 (2/7). M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3m x\u00fac khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn &ldquo;t\u00ed hon&rdquo; Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u1eabn \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch B\u1ec9 2-0 sau 7 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o l\u00fac tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, B\u1ec9 l\u1ea1i v\u00f9ng l\u00ean d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd thua d\u1ec5 bao nhi\u00eau th\u00ec g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u0169ng ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau v\u1edbi 2 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Jan Vertonghen v\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng (ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 22 gi\u00e2y), Nacer Chadli k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Du-am-Bi-3-2-Nhat-Ban-Quy-do-no-Samurai-loi-cam-on!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mang l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ec9 sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 7 ph\u00fat, Genki Haraguchi v\u00e0 Takashi Inui \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt l\u00e2ng l\u00e2ng v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ee7i h\u1ed5 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. Sau \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina, T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ed3i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean trong g\u1ea7n 70 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua. Ch\u00fa th\u1ecf ham ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua r\u00f9a, nh\u01b0ng &ldquo;Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf&rdquo; v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i &ldquo;Samurai xanh&rdquo;. Vertonghen, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ed9c l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi b\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng 2-1 ph\u00fat 69 d\u00f9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhat Ban dan truoc Bi 2-0\" title=\"Nhat Ban dan truoc Bi 2-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Nhat-Ban-dan-truoc-Bi-2-0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn 2-0 \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n5 ph\u00fat sau, Eden Hazard xoay tr\u1edf kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ea1t v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t ng\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ec3 Fellaini g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, B\u1ec9 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng. Qu\u1ea3 c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a Thomas Meunier k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00fa nh\u1ea5c ch\u00e2n t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Chadli d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 c\u00f9ng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho B\u1ec9. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00e1c. Sau hi\u1ec7p 1, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00e3 th\u1ebf, kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc c\u00f2n c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. V\u00e0 khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tinh th\u1ea7n cho 30 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi vuot qua Nhat vao tu ket\" title=\"Bi vuot qua Nhat vao tu ket\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Bi-vuot-qua-Nhat-vao-tu-ket.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng sai. Trong hi\u1ec7p 1, ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng. Nh\u01b0ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn cho t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0 v\u1eabn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 l\u1eebng kh\u1eebng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u00ed th\u1ebf v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 h\u01a1n 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n, c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1eed l\u00fd r\u1ea5t h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c. Suy ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i theo B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ecbu 2 b\u00e0n thua n\u1eb7ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m g\u00ec 2 c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a v\u00f5 s\u0129 quy\u1ec1n anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tinh than Bi co van de\" title=\"tinh than Bi co van de\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/tinh-than-Bi-co-van-de.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1ee7 quan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh World Cup 2018, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i t\u1edbi VCK, B\u1ec9 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez may m\u1eafn ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng &ldquo;nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u&rdquo; Gibraltar, \u0110\u1ea3o S\u00edp r\u1ed3i Estonia \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng Hy L\u1ea1p, Bosnia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1edbi Nga (th\u1eafng 9, h\u00f2a 1, h\u01a1n ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi VCK, B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1i y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 Martinez kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ra th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u01b0a d\u1ed1c l\u00f2ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9. Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00eam 2/7, d\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u1edbi d\u1ea1y cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc th\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan. Khi trong \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 \u00fd ngh\u0129 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi vs Nhat Lukaku va Kagawa\" title=\"Bi vs Nhat Lukaku va Kagawa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Bi-vs-Nhat-Lukaku-va-Kagawa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lukaku c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd mang \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 t\u1ec9nh gi\u1ea5c. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n t\u1eeb HLV Martinez trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. Th\u1eadt may l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m k\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra: B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 Brazil?<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa, ngay 1h ng\u00e0y 7/7 t\u1edbi th\u00f4i, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. C\u00e1c C\u0110V B\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc r\u00fat ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. \u1ede m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u1eefng Samurai xanh b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 th\u1ee9c t\u1ec9nh k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so Bi 3-2 Nhat Ban\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Thong-so-Bi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-roberto-martinez-phat-bieu-ve-tran-bi-vs-nhat-ban-421-190238.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, HLV B\u1ec9 n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban-421-190237.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/eden-hazard-thua-nhan-bi-tung-run-so-nhat-ban-465-190236.html\">Eden Hazard th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn B\u1ec9 t\u1eebng run s\u1ee3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nhat-ban-tiec-vi-khong-thang-bi-465-190233.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd B\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"836","checkdouble":"190243"},{"date":"07:16 03/07","title":"Willian cay c\u00fa khi Brazil b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/willian.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Brazil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Selecao ch\u01a1i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Brazil b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 qua \u0111\u00f3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Brazil vs Mexico khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tite \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 B\u1ec9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho 8 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Brazil sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Brazil sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Willian-phat-bieu-ve-Brazil-sau-chien-thang-truoc-Mexico-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Brazil b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p trong kho\u1ea3ng 20 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. Sau \u0111\u00f3 khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng Selecao co \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1ed3n \u00e9p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n l\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Brazil, song c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Selecao \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico song Brazil \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 Mexico kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf samba.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Brazil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Selecao ch\u01a1i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian duoc khen ngoi boi tro ly DT Brazil, Sylvinho sau tran thang Mexico.\" title=\"Willian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i b\u1edfi tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u0110T Brazil, Sylvinho sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Mexico.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/willian-brazil-can-bang-trong-tan-cong-va-phong-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y th\u00ec s\u1ebd r\u00f5. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n Brazil x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Neymar m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/willian-duoc-khen-ngoi-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-cua-dt-brazil-465-190225.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sylvinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Willian</span>, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Tite \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"835","checkdouble":"190246"},{"date":"07:02 03/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (3/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-372018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 3/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/Lich_thi_dau_World_Cup_2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"> L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t</span><br />\r\nC\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 14.6 \u0